{"tid":1606382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會出嚟嘅，入一入嚟！","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:55:37.000Z","uid":198113,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bece9f9e50eed6ed0de0ba7736bae6920057da","tid":1606382,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"你知唔知道點解而家班狗可以咁惡？就係因為你哋對佢哋太過仁慈。對敵人仁慈，就係對自己殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n你哋仲記唔記得女義士喺尖沙咀比狗射中眼？仲記唔記得岳義士為咗救人而比狗打到爆曬缸？<br />\n<br />\n當你仲覺得班狗殘忍、冷血、兇殘嘅時候，咁係因為你哋未夠佢哋殘忍，未夠佢哋冷血，未夠佢哋兇殘<br />\n<br />\n眾手足們，聽日係時候突破自己心理關口。依家香港人以至全世界嘅人都已經核彈都唔割，我哋冇需要再擔心民意會流失<br />\n<br />\n你睇吓之前我哋仲未齊裝嘅時候，都已經追住啲狗嚟打，點解依家我哋齊晒裝嘅時候，反而會驚咗班狗？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3Wy63G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3Wy63G.gif&h=4130405e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmJQ9hd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmJQ9hd.gif&h=be89ef4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYdYyKj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYdYyKj.gif&h=32e0a23b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEA4uhG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEA4uhG.gif&h=c243cefa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrzAAYe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrzAAYe.gif&h=365a220f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5b4QpRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5b4QpRA.gif&h=9c7351d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OThZicx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOThZicx.gif&h=6194acd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0S4H0qT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0S4H0qT.gif&h=061977d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/30/210850_7e87024a889951815bf57a1ab6483d30.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F30%2F210850_7e87024a889951815bf57a1ab6483d30.gif&h=17808195&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEbn0q9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEbn0q9.gif&h=931a53fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzJtVZv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzJtVZv.jpg&h=3fb5afc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">歡迎手足放更多治癒圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n遇到班狗嘅時候<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></strong></span>驚，然後即刻向後退。嘗試號召所有人，一齊向前推。啲狗一定最驚你埋身戰，所以先係咁放催淚彈同開槍。所以懇請大家，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日一定要向前推！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋聽日再冇輸嘅餘地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不過切記，請勿戀戰，安全至上</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e2a8fb1e9c13294e3cc06574d370ef33246a504","tid":1606382,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"推完呢個post，之後聽日再推"},{"pid":"a910bfc8e7437c9fe29fb4a5dd3c7b3979803a52","tid":1606382,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"聽日大家要一齊有規律及有節奏地大叫：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">向前推</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"afe149e5cdde086a38976ab4b04eead60059ad04","tid":1606382,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"向前推 向前推"},{"pid":"aaca30e7aad056cc908a9df2f42f8c22025f7459","tid":1606382,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫手推？"},{"pid":"a6574586f0fbfc46b132d6ac5756488bc2cfe492","tid":1606382,"uid":1266